227
00:15:13,679 --> 00:15:15,874
Sweetie, I'll be fine.

228
00:15:15,948 --> 00:15:18,815
Let me hold your ring for you.

229
00:15:18,884 --> 00:15:20,852
Almost forgot.

230
00:15:24,323 --> 00:15:26,416
Don't make any statements.

231
00:15:26,492 --> 00:15:28,585
