238
00:15:53,852 --> 00:15:57,117
<i>Anything you'd like to say
toJoynes's victims, Mr. Colby?</i>

239
00:15:57,189 --> 00:16:00,158
Can we get a statement?
Anything at all, please, Mr. Colby.

240
00:16:00,225 --> 00:16:02,887
<i>Anything. A nything you'd like to say
to theJoynes family?</i>

241
00:16:06,365 --> 00:16:10,563
